ActTerritorial Lands Act
PrecisORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (DEH CHO FIRST NATIONS, N.W.T.) - which provides for (a) the repeal of Order in Council P.C. 2003-1230 of August 13, 2003, and (b) the withdrawal from disposal of certain lands in order to facilitate the conclusion of the Deh Cho First Nations Final Agreement.
